        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
            <head>Scope and Content </head>
            <p>Memorandum of agreement between the state of Virginia and Cowell, a Philadelphia
                gunsmith, to produce 2,000 rampart muskets. Specifics, price, and terms of payment
                set. Signed by James Madison, Theodorick Bland, and Meriwether Smith. Certificate of
                compliance signed by Thomas Pleasants based on information supplied by George
                Newhan. </p>
        </scopecontent>
